  <name>Solr</name>
  <summary>The Solr extension is an extremely fast, light-weight, feature-rich library that 
allows PHP developers to communicate effectively with Solr server instances.
  </summary>
  <description>It effectively simplifies the process of interacting with Solr using PHP.</description>
